org.wso2.transport.http.netty.message

Class Http2PushPromise

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.transport.http.netty.message.Http2PushPromise

  • public class Http2PushPromise
extends Object
    Http2PushPromise represents a HTTP/2 PUSH_PROMISE frame. This represents both HTTP/2 push promises received from a server as well as the push promises suppose to be delivered to a client. A PUSH_PROMISE should not be sent by a client.
